I am being pedantic, but that would be a <i>function</i> and not an <i>alias</i>.<p>This one is simple enough to be defined as an alias:<p><pre><code>    alias gitdiff=&#x27;git diff --patience --ignore-space-at-eol -b -w --ignore-blank-lines&#x27;
</code></pre>
